#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.issubclass_:4
msgid ""
"`issubclass_` is equivalent to the Python built-in ``issubclass``, except "
"that it returns False instead of raising a TypeError if one of the arguments "
"is not a class."
msgstr ""

